==English==
===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Pangasinan'''
# a [[province]] of the [[Philippines]] in the island of [[Luzon]]
# the [[language]] (of the [[Austonesian]] family) spoken in the Philippines, primarily in the province of Pangasinan.
# a native speaker of the Pangasinan language.
===Adjective===
'''Pangasinan'''
# Pertaining to the people who speak the Pangasinan language.
